Package org.glassfish.jersey.server.wadl.internal.generators.resourcedoc.model

package org.glassfish.jersey.server.wadl.internal.generators.resourcedoc.model
Jersey server-side WADL internal JAXB beans used for generation of resource documentation with wadl generators.
